    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>The difference between RMI and RPC is that:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>RMI</strong> as the name indicates Remote Method Invoking: it invokes a method or an object. And</li>\n<li><strong>RPC</strong> it invokes a function.</li>\n</ul>\n"
